column1: #Text=The host Utah Jazz defeated the Los Angeles Lakers , 96 - 89 , at Vivint Smart Home Arena on Friday .
#Text=The Jazz ( 1 - 1 ) have been one of the best teams in the NBA this season , but they were able to prevail with a win .
#Text=In fact , the Jazz led for the majority of the game , as they outscored the Lakers by 16 in the fourth quarter .
#Text=Rebounding was key for the Jazz , as they held the Lakers to 38 percent from the field and 24 percent from three - point range .
